## Practice Exercises (Lesson 4)

1. Har department ka naam aur us department mein employees ki total count dikhao (LEFT JOIN use karke, empty departments bhi dikhein).
2. Sirf un departments ko dikhao jinki average salary 60000 se zyada hai.
3. Total kitne employees hain jinka koi department assign nahi hai? (COUNT + WHERE IS NULL)
4. Har department ka highest aur lowest salary dikhao, sirf un departments ke liye jinme 1 se zyada employee hai (HAVING COUNT > 1).

